Package ohos.bluetooth.ble

Class BleScanFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.bluetooth.ble.BleScanFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Sequenceable

    public final class BleScanFilter
extends Object
implements Sequenceable
    Filters BLE scanning results.

    The criteria for filtering scanning results can be set.

    Constructing a filter requires the address, name, service data, service UUID, and manufacturer of a peripheral device.

    Since:
    1
